University Account Management 

A webapp that is designed in (technologies) that will be an account management system like RAMSS,
but the design and functionality will be completely reengineered to make it more usable and which 
requires minimal number of clicks to perform the same task as compared to other account management systems. 

Requirements Document

1
Students need to be able to view account summary 
  Task
  Make account summary page as a hyperlink on the main page
    Days 1
  Task
  Design the Account Summary Page with information like remaining balance, tax information, financial aid, payment summary, etc.
    Days 2

2
Students need to be able to see their academic records and graduation requirements, while being able to enroll in required future courses

3
Enrolling/Swapping/Dropping courses

4
View/Change Personal Information

5
View Schedule

6
Request a Letter
